        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer541995268" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7942324144714030832">Put Temperance Brennan from &quot;Bones&quot; in the Plantagenet era, make her a less sympathetic and more inconsistent character, and add a heaping helping of heavy-handed WOMEN HAD IT TERRIBLY BAD BACK THEN AND THE PEOPLE RESPONSIBLE SHOULD BE ASHAMED OF THEMSELVES, AND IF I (THE AUTHOR IN THE GUISE OF THE MAIN CHARACTER) WERE IN CHARGE THINGS WOULD BE BETTER, and you have this book. I wanted to find out whodunit, then I did. The last 40 pages then became unnecessary. I&apos;m glad I picked this up for only </span>
  <span id="freeText7942324144714030832" style="display:none">Put Temperance Brennan from "Bones" in the Plantagenet era, make her a less sympathetic and more inconsistent character, and add a heaping helping of heavy-handed WOMEN HAD IT TERRIBLY BAD BACK THEN AND THE PEOPLE RESPONSIBLE SHOULD BE ASHAMED OF THEMSELVES, AND IF I (THE AUTHOR IN THE GUISE OF THE MAIN CHARACTER) WERE IN CHARGE THINGS WOULD BE BETTER, and you have this book. I wanted to find out whodunit, then I did. The last 40 pages then became unnecessary. I'm glad I picked this up for only $1. The smug superiority, plodding mystery, and awful people populating this book are just too much. </span>
  <a data-text-id="7942324144714030832" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

