    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer110655582" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13380714229568959469">Somewhat slower paced than the first because much of it takes place in a convent. Murders compete with the mores of the cloister. If you are interested in the historical period of Henry II&apos;s England this is no problem. Otherwise, you had better not take it on summer holiday.<br/><br/>An interesting sidelight is the plot&apos;s investment in the status and tribulations of being a woman of any class at this period of time.</span>
